Licensing

This repository contains two independent CMake projects under different
licenses:

- `aoa-dgt/` (AOADGT) — GNU General Public License v3.0. The complete license
  text is in `aoa-dgt/COPYING`.
- `aoa-ntt/` (newckks) — MIT License. The complete license text is in
  `aoa-ntt/LICENSE`.

Each subdirectory’s license applies to the source files in that subtree. When
you copy or distribute code, follow the terms of the license that covers the
files you use.
